///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
usage: run_keywords.py [-h] [-p PDF] [-t TXT] [-s STOPWORDS] [-l RUS/ENG]
                       [-o OUTPUT]

Extracting keywords from a pdf or txt file.

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -p PDF, --pdf PDF     Path to pdf file, metavar = ""*.pdf""
  -t TXT, --txt TXT     Path to txt file, metavar = ""*.txt""
  -s STOPWORDS, --stopwords STOPWORDS
                        Path to a file with a stopwords
  -l RUS/ENG, --language RUS/ENG
                        Specifies a language for a text or PDF document
  -o OUTPUT, --output OUTPUT
                        Path to output file

///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
usage: run_statistics.py [-h] [-p PDF] [-t TXT] [-s STOPWORDS] [-l RUS/ENG]
                         [-o OUTPUT]

Making a statistics about a pdf or txt file.

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -p PDF, --pdf PDF     Path to pdf file, metavar = ""*.pdf""
  -t TXT, --txt TXT     Path to txt file, metavar = ""*.txt""
  -s STOPWORDS, --stopwords STOPWORDS
                        Path to a file with a stopwords
  -l RUS/ENG, --language RUS/ENG
                        Specifies a language for a text or PDF document
  -o OUTPUT, --output OUTPUT
                        Path to output file
